card.desc:
Must Have

‌

As a user,

I want to be able to edit a saved project

So that I can pick up from my last rap.

‌

Given I select a project from my list,

When I click to edit it,

Then I can view the lyrics already added to the project.
card.name: Editing Projects

card.desc:
Must Have

‌

As a user,

I want to be able to delete my projects,

So that I can keep my project lists tidy.

‌

Given I select a project from my list,

When I click to delete it,

Then it is removed.
card.name: Deleting Projects

old.desc: Users can play back audio of their rap they’ve previously recorded.

card.desc:
Must Have

‌

As a user,

I want to create a new rap project,

So that I can start drafting some new lyrics.

‌

Given I select to start a new project,

When I start creating my rap,

Then I have my project saved to my account.
card.name: Create Rap

old.desc: A variety of beats available to the user in the app

card.desc:
Must Have

‌

As a user,

I want a variety of beats to choose from,

So that I can choose the right one for my rap.

‌

Given I choose a beat to listen to,

When I select that beat in the list of options,

Then I can hear the beat as I rap.
card.name: Beat Variety

old.desc: Users are able to listen to and rap over beats within the app

card.desc:
Must Have

‌

As a user,

I want to listen to a beat when using the app,

So that I can rap to it.

‌

Given I begin a rap,

When I click to play the beat,

Then I can hear the beat as I'm rapping.
card.name: Built-In Beats

old.desc: Users can record audio through the app and save it.

Must Have

As a user,

I want to record my freestyles into text,

So that i can view them at a later date.

‌

Given I begin performing a rap,

When I click the record button,

Then I have my lyrics saved in the app.
card.name: Recording Audio

Then I am registered as a new user.
